      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, ive had asthma for years but lately i feel like i'm getting out of breath way too easy. even just walking to the kitchen for water makes me feel winded. is this just part of getting older or do i need to change my inhaler dose?",
      "source": "evaluator"
