      "content": "It's important not to ignore worsening symptoms, as they could indicate a change in your asthma control. While age can impact asthma, frequent and severe symptoms should prompt a consultation with your healthcare provider. They can assess your situation, evaluate your inhaler use, and possibly adjust the dosage or suggest other treatments.",
